summary: The document is a dispatch under the President John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992, detailing the transmission of unused operational documentation from a Havana operation back to Headquarters. It includes specifics on identity cards and lamination materials, such as cellophane sheets, linked to the Department of Justice of the Commonwealth of Puerto Rico.
key_findings: Document is part of the JFK Assassination Records Act of 1992.
Details operational documentation not utilized in a Havana operation.
Contains information on identity cards and materials for lamination.
Connected to the Department of Justice of the Commonwealth of Puerto Rico.
